Class cObjectBase

java.lang.Object
Data.cObjectBase
Direct Known Subclasses:
cGalaxy, cPlanet, cStar
public class cObjectBase extends Object
Base class for all named objects in the system. Provides common functionality for objects that have a name and can be converted to string representation. This class serves as the foundation for all astronomical objects in the StarViewer application.
